q3n (1.1.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix: plugins (fortune/cite) now load correctly in the installed .deb package
  * Fix: plugins now bundled in AppImage (app/ added to PyInstaller datas)
  * Fix: AppImage plugin discovery handles PyInstaller frozen executable path
  * Fix: fortune pop-out uses relative import, works in all install contexts
  * Fix: double-clicking a .q3n file in a file manager now opens it (handles %F arg)
  * Fix: build-appimage.sh no longer depends on web/ directory for icon
  * Fix: source tarballs exclude web/ and .github/ via .gitattributes
  * Chore: debian/control description corrected; Recommends: python3-pip removed
  * Add: Scriptorium warm dark theme shipped as the default GUI theme
  * Bump version to 1.1.4

